                Mr. Thorne
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-5c991a62-d4ce-408e-b66d-4f4ef74724c7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
